SELECT a.* , b.id AS link_id , b.link_name , b.link_mobilephone, c.name AS branch_name, d.para_name AS car_type_name, e.para_name AS car_nature_name FROM T_Cm_Car a LEFT JOIN dbo.T_Cm_Link b ON a.car_link = b.id LEFT JOIN dbo.T_Cm_Branch c ON a.branch_id = c.id LEFT JOIN dbo.T_Cm_Code d ON d.para_value=a.car_type AND d.para_type='car_type' LEFT JOIN dbo.T_Cm_Code e ON e.para_value=a.car_type AND e.para_type='car_nature'

SELECT * , b.name AS branch_name , c.para_name AS sex_name , d.para_name AS status_name FROM T_Cm_Emp a LEFT JOIN dbo.T_Cm_Branch b ON a.branch_id = b.id LEFT JOIN dbo.T_Cm_Code c ON c.para_value = a.sex_ind AND c.para_type = 'sex' LEFT JOIN dbo.T_Cm_Code d ON d.para_value = a.status AND d.para_type = 'office_statue'
